Amanda Holden looked phenomenal as she stripped down to her bikini while soaking up the sun poolside while aborad. The Heart FM host, 51, filmed herself dancing around a crystal-clear swimming pool as she stripped down to reveal a tiny striped bikini. The mother-of-two coated herself in a shimmery sunscreen to protect her body from the sun's rays as she made the most of her time away. Amanda showcased her flawless tan after removing a white shirt, black shorts and flip-flops. She wore her blonde hair in a straight, sleek style and donned a pair of oversized, black sunglasses.